[postmark: Dec. 14, 1982]
Dear Jack,
Thank god for Christmas to remind us to say "Hello" and send our heartfelt wishes to you and Gladys -- we pray she's doing well! Have a glorious Christmas and New Year!
Love you,
Jim & Edie McCormick
Jack Conroy 
701 Fisk Avenue
Moberly, MO 65270
